<li><a href="http://www.archive.org/details/lehrer" class="external text" title="http://www.archive.org/details/lehrer" rel="nofollow">A video recording of five songs performed by Lehrer</a> (for <a href="/wiki/Irving_Kaplansky" title="Irving Kaplansky">Irving Kaplansky</a> in 1997)</li>
<li><a href="http://home.teleport.com/~osh/leher.htm" class="external text" title="http://home.teleport.com/~osh/leher.htm" rel="nofollow">Tom Lehrer: The man, his myth and his music</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.tomlehrer.org" class="external text" title="http://www.tomlehrer.org" rel="nofollow">A Tom Lehrer and Tom Foolery web page</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.casualhacker.net/tom.lehrer/jmazner/lehrhtml.html" class="external text" title="http://www.casualhacker.net/tom.lehrer/jmazner/lehrhtml.html" rel="nofollow">Tom Lehrer: The Political Musician Who Wasn't</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.sfweekly.com/issues/2000-04-19/feature.html" class="external text" title="http://www.sfweekly.com/issues/2000-04-19/feature.html" rel="nofollow">An interview with SF Weekly</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.paul-lehrman.com/insider/1997/12insiderfulltext.html" class="external text" title="http://www.paul-lehrman.com/insider/1997/12insiderfulltext.html" rel="nofollow">Conversation with Tom Lehrer</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.hti.umich.edu/u/umhistmath/Lobachevsky.mp3" class="external text" title="http://www.hti.umich.edu/u/umhistmath/Lobachevsky.mp3" rel="nofollow">Lobachevsky song</a> by Tom Lehrer, in <a href="/wiki/MP3" title="MP3">MP3</a> format.</li>
<li><a href="http://allmusic.com/cg/amg.dll?p=amg&amp;sql=11:xye997b7krgt" class="external text" title="http://allmusic.com/cg/amg.dll?p=amg&amp;sql=11:xye997b7krgt" rel="nofollow">Tom Lehrer</a> at <a href="/wiki/Allmusic" title="Allmusic">Allmusic</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0499875/" class="external text" title="http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0499875/" rel="nofollow">Tom Lehrer</a> at the <a href="/wiki/Internet_Movie_Database" title="Internet Movie Database">Internet Movie Database</a></li>
<li><a href="http://curvebank.calstatela.edu/newmath/newmath.htm" class="external text" title="http://curvebank.calstatela.edu/newmath/newmath.htm" rel="nofollow">Tom Lehrer Deposit #10</a> Authorized website that plays Lehrer's entire song "New Math" and encourages you to download the track or buy the CD.</li>
</ul>


